# Jenkins_ci-cd_pipeline
Jenkins end to end project 


Project 1: Jenkins End-to-End CI/CD Pipeline
Overview
Implemented an end-to-end CI/CD pipeline using Jenkins to automate build, code quality analysis, artifact management, and deployment processes.
Tools Used
Git
Jenkins
Maven
SonarQube
Nexus Repository
Apache Tomcat
Workflow
Source code pushed to Git repository.
Jenkins pipeline triggered automatically.
Maven builds the application and generates artifacts.
SonarQube performs code quality analysis.
Artifacts stored in Nexus Repository.
Application deployed to Tomcat server.
Email notifications sent for build and deployment status.
Key Achievements
Automated build and deployment process.
Improved code quality through SonarQube integration.
Centralized artifact management using Nexus.
